The Desi
Heritage Food Validator is a specialized tool dedicated to preserving the authenticity of India’s vast and ancient culinary landscape. From the spice-heavy kitchens of the North to the coastal delicacies of the South, this project ensures that traditional recipes are honored and validated against true heritage standards.
In a world where Indian cuisine is often generalized, this validator acts as a digital safeguard for the specific techniques, ingredients, and soul that define authentic Indian cooking.
